snippet.title: McDonald's lost Nintendo DS eCDP Training Game: Full Playthrough!
snippet.description:
Here's our full-length, first-ever playthrough of the long lost McDonald's eCrew Development Program, as detailed in this video: https://youtu.be/-e6xOBCAVvA
UPDATE: Decided to make this video free for everyone for the time being! Enjoy! :)
More bonus videos: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7JcnzNnpnN0&list=PLGFiGO64XRnjhzze6RlQxWnpcbCJwrubX&index=4&t=1s

Confused? Watch the full documentary: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-e6xOBCAVvA

Download the McDonald's Japan eCrew Development Program Employee Training Nintendo DS ROM (and save file): https://archive.org/details/mcdonalds-japan-ecdp-rom-training-nintendo-ds-cartridge-dump
